creator: Red Canoe Credit Union
descriptionHtml:
Red Canoe Credit Union is bringing you Mobile Banking to your Android Device. You’ll have easy access to your accounts in Online Banking with this app. Benefits include:

Balances – view account balances and transaction history
Transfers – transfer between your accounts or to another member
Bill Payer – pay bills and view recent payments
Mobile Deposit – use your phone to take a photo of a check and deposit it directly to your qualified account
Locations – get directions to Red Canoe branches, shared branch locations and ATMs.

Mobile Banking is FREE and SECURE. Security includes the latest in SSL encryption and is backed by Online Banking secure sign-on.
descriptionShort: Try the new Android App for Red Canoe Credit Union!
